    <p>You retain full ownership of all content you create using Polynote, including:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Audio recordings</li>
      <li>Transcriptions generated from your recordings</li>
      <li>Auto-generated study materials (flashcards, quizzes, key terms)</li>
      <li>Folders and organizational structures</li>
