  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>4. Recording Consent and Legal Compliance</h2>
    <p>You are solely responsible for obtaining all necessary consents before recording:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Obtain consent from all participants before recording any conversation, lecture, or meeting</li>
      <li>Comply with federal, state, and local recording laws (some jurisdictions require all-party consent)</li>
      <li>Respect copyright and intellectual property rights of recorded content</li>
      <li>Do not record in situations where recording is prohibited</li>
      <li>Use recordings ethically and respect privacy of others</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Failure to obtain proper consent may result in legal liability. Polynote is not responsible for your use of the recording features.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
