    <p>Polynote offers optional integration with Google services:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Google Sign-In: Optional authentication (not required to use the app)</li>
      <li>Google Calendar: Optional scheduling and event creation (requires explicit consent)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>When using Google services, you agree to Google's Terms of Service and Privacy Policy. You can disconnect Google services at any time without losing locally stored data. All core features work fully offline without Google integration.</p>
